flowchart TD
    Start([Admin Access Requested]) --> NavAdminLogin[Navigate to /admin-login]
    NavAdminLogin --> EnterAdminCreds[Enter Admin Credentials]
    EnterAdminCreds --> VerifyRole{Is User Admin?}
    
    VerifyRole -- No --> Reject[Show Access Denied]
    VerifyRole -- Yes --> NavAdmin[Navigate to /admin]
    
    NavAdmin --> Dashboard[Admin Dashboard Overview]
    
    Dashboard --> Action1[Manage Cars]
    Action1 --> EditCars[Add/Edit/Delete Vehicles]
    
    Dashboard --> Action2[Manage Users]
    Action2 --> EditUsers[View/Ban User Accounts]
    
    Dashboard --> Action3[View Activity Monitor]
    Action3 --> CheckLogs[Monitor site activity and traffic]
    
    Dashboard --> Action4[Manage Bookings]
    Action4 --> OrderStatus[Update Order & Rental Statuses]
